  &#x3C;input type=&#x22;password&#x22; id=&#x22;labelin_input2&#x22;&#x3E;
&#x3C;/div&#x3E;</code></pre>

      <hr>

		  <h3 class="center">Submit button</h3>

      <br>

      <div class="submit">
      	<input type="submit" value="Submit button">
      </div>

      <pre><code>&#x3C;div class=&#x22;submit&#x22;&#x3E;
  &#x3C;input type=&#x22;submit&#x22; value=&#x22;Submit button&#x22;&#x3E;
